</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>元宇宙導致家居意外上升　英國保險索賠增加 31%</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/15/aviva-vr/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=aviva-vr</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 15 Feb 2022 07:53:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Metaverse]]></category><category><![CDATA[vr]]></category><category><![CDATA[元宇宙]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086347</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>時興元宇宙，連帶 VR（虛擬實景）裝置亦大行其道。帶上眼鏡後，往往今人看不清現實，容易出錯。近日，有保險公司公 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>時興元宇宙，連帶 VR（虛擬實景）裝置亦大行其道。帶上眼鏡後，往往今人看不清現實，容易出錯。近日，有保險公司公布了新數據，指家居意外頻生，連同家庭財產索賠金額亦上升。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086350" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VR-Revolution-1-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VR-Revolution-1-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VR-Revolution-1-768x402.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/VR-Revolution-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">▲網絡圖片</span></p><p>英國第二大保險公司 Aviva 表示，去年 VR 裝置相關意外，平均索賠金額約 880 美元（約 6,800 港元），家庭財產索賠增加了 31%，是自 2016 年增加了 68%。</p><p>Aviva 英國財產索賠主管 Kelly Whittington 指：「隨著新遊戲和 VR 眼鏡等小型裝備更為流行，我們經常看到以上情況在客戶的索賠裡出現。」明顯地，趨勢已逐漸形成，Aviva 已著手處理與 VR 裝置有關的賠償，並預計全年將有更多同類事件發生。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2022/feb/12/rising-popularity-of-vr-headsets-sparks-31-rise-in-insurance-claims">The Guardian</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><p><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=e6lXUtBNYzY:sIzK0xXD3bU:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=e6lXUtBNYzY:sIzK0xXD3bU:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>保時捷攜瑞士初創開發 Virtual Roads　手機記錄真實街道變賽車遊戲賽道</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/15/porsche/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=porsche</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 15 Feb 2022 07:41:39 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[ar]]></category><category><![CDATA[porsche]]></category><category><![CDATA[virtual racing]]></category><category><![CDATA[vr]]></category><category><![CDATA[保時捷]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086330</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>保時捷與瑞士初創公司合作開發遊戲軟件，讓車主可以將日常駕駛的道路化為遊戲中的賽道，而用家只需一部智能手機即可做 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>保時捷與瑞士初創公司合作開發遊戲軟件，讓車主可以將日常駕駛的道路化為遊戲中的賽道，而用家只需一部智能手機即可做到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086334 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/8fd1d609ca7274960a4b50bbc07b8546-1-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/8fd1d609ca7274960a4b50bbc07b8546-1-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/8fd1d609ca7274960a4b50bbc07b8546-1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/8fd1d609ca7274960a4b50bbc07b8546-1.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086335 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/01d1bad3f39a34b2e965dcb7308668e7-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/01d1bad3f39a34b2e965dcb7308668e7-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/01d1bad3f39a34b2e965dcb7308668e7-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/01d1bad3f39a34b2e965dcb7308668e7.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：保時捷</p><p>瑞士初創公司 Way Ahead Technologies 將此項目命名為 Virtual Roads，預計這款新電子遊戲需要幾個月甚至幾年的時間開發。賽車模擬器中的賽道必需經專家使用雷射精確掃描，才可把路面數碼化。駕駛者可使用智能手機特定的應用程式記錄任何路線，只要將手機固定在檔風玻璃後即可。然後，應用程式會將錄下來的環境轉換成程式數據，數據會自動傳輸到虛擬世界。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086336 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/30b0cb467b4644dbdc6304627fe2b333-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/30b0cb467b4644dbdc6304627fe2b333-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/30b0cb467b4644dbdc6304627fe2b333-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/30b0cb467b4644dbdc6304627fe2b333.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086337 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/5ac7b00e4ab8e778cab40ea5047581d1-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/5ac7b00e4ab8e778cab40ea5047581d1-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/5ac7b00e4ab8e778cab40ea5047581d1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/5ac7b00e4ab8e778cab40ea5047581d1.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲只要將手機固定在檔風玻璃後即可記錄任何路線（圖片來源：保時捷）</p><p>料程式可捕捉道路及其周圍的特徵，如防撞護欄和樹木等。程式會盡量還原地形和街道特徵。當中，在街道上經過的行人不會被納入傳送範圍。新應用程序生成的每條獨特路線檔案目前與包括 Assetto Corsa 在內的許多賽車遊戲相容，而路線可在模擬器和手機應用程式上體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086338 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0e922209b22f65e1011cd40254c53109-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0e922209b22f65e1011cd40254c53109-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0e922209b22f65e1011cd40254c53109-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0e922209b22f65e1011cd40254c53109.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086340 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/318b600f6c2ac2a1fb05022ab13cbc20-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/318b600f6c2ac2a1fb05022ab13cbc20-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/318b600f6c2ac2a1fb05022ab13cbc20-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/318b600f6c2ac2a1fb05022ab13cbc20.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：保時捷</p><p>Way Ahead Technologies 的 Roger Rueegg 更表示：「經過幾年的開發工作，我們的軟體現在非常先進，可以在不到一個小時的時間內將長達 8 公里的虛擬道路的路線數碼化，具體取決於路線的複雜程度。我們目前也在考慮其他選項和功能。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086341 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/f75028b467c8ee58c4a7afba597650af-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/f75028b467c8ee58c4a7afba597650af-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/f75028b467c8ee58c4a7afba597650af-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/f75028b467c8ee58c4a7afba597650af.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1086343 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-168x580.jpeg" alt="" width="168" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-168x580.jpeg 168w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-261x900.jpeg 261w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-768x2648.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-445x1536.jpeg 445w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-594x2048.jpeg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/453a20ef1dfd0e9b9311dd979c3cf046-scaled.jpeg 464w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 168px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：保時捷</p><p>來源：<a href="https://newsroom.porsche.com/en_US/2022/technology/porsche-way-ahead-technologies-innovative-software-solution-virtual-roads-video-game-27382.html">保時捷</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><p><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
