</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900  Bose 獨家音效技術+ Dolby Atmos 支援</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/15/bose-soundbar-900/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bose-soundbar-900</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 15 Feb 2022 04:30:38 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[影音產品]]></category><category><![CDATA[bose]]></category><category><![CDATA[Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085240</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>在電視收看 Netflix、Disney+ 等影音串流服務，除了一個大電視之外，用家對於電影音響愈來愈重視，希 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在電視收看 Netflix、Disney+ 等影音串流服務，除了一個大電視之外，用家對於電影音響愈來愈重視，希望有一個 Soundbar 能發揮電影本身的 Dolby Atmos 音效。<a href="https://bit.ly/35tDSJS">Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900</a> 就因此應運而生，它擁有獨家空間處理技術 (spatial technologies) ，可把樂器、對白與音效分開，分別傳送到房間的每一個角落，例如最左側、最右側、頭頂等等，造到更逼真的現場感。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_White_004_RGB.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_003_RGB.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-1280x702.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-768x421.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-1536x842.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-2048x1123.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_09_CMYK-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900 型格出眾，外觀採用條形圓角設計，環繞著金屬格柵，細心留意之下，可發現每一個揚聲器的整個頂部，都覆蓋著強化玻璃，再加上優雅的燈條設計，與包覆式金屬的外殼互相襯托，放在你的電視面前，其漆黑高貴外觀仿如家居的其中一個擺設。然而這件藝術品的內裡，卻有 7 個揚聲器組成的列陣，精準地佈局在長條形 Soundbar 的每一個部份。除了特定發聲單元、薄型單元製造出有層次感的電影聲效，Soundbar 更有 2 個全新偶極向上發射單元，能夠營造出從頭頂上方發出來的音效，你毋須在天花設置揚聲器，都可為電影聲效帶來「高度感」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-1280x708.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-768x425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-1536x850.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-2048x1133.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_14_RGB-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_013_RGB.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>Bose 獨有技術提升音效層次感</h2><p>為了令電影聲效更具層次感，<a href="https://bit.ly/35tDSJS">Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900</a> 採用了獨家 PhaseGuide 音效技術，Soundbar 可讓你感覺到從沒有揚聲器的地方，都有聲音傳來。例如從上方而來的直升機，演員從你的身上跳過等等，都可從聲音表現出來。在收看歌劇或演唱會影片，假如歌手在你的中間偏左位置演奏，你可在聲效上感受到聲音從中間偏左傳來。Soundbar 不再只是一條長方形金屬條，而是能夠為你帶來四方八面而來的聲效。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Remote_002_RGB.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900 支援 Dolby Atmos 杜比全景聲技術，能讓 Netflix、Disney+ 等串流服務的現場聲效，能在你的電視面前重現。Bose 更加入了獨家 TrueSpace 技術，就算你收看的電影沒有 Dolby Atmos 訊號（例如立體聲或 5.1 聲效），其晶片會對聲音進行分析，重新混合音訊，在音場中創造出高度感，提升電影觀賞體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_009_RGB-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>即使是觀看一般節目與播放音樂，Soundbar 都有專用 Bose QuietPort 技術處理音源，令音效的低音能夠精準重現，再加上獨有的 ADAPTiQ 智能音色調校系統，能夠根據家居佈置情況，自動調整音色。不同用戶有不同的家居擺設，也能感受到最佳的聆聽體驗。</p><h2>強大連接能力：輕鬆連線手機電腦、更多揚聲器</h2><p>Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900 擁有十分強大的連接能力，只需要一條 HDMI eARC 線，就可連接電視，它更可藍牙配對智能手機、電腦、平板電腦等等，你亦可通過 Wi-Fi 連接 Spotify Connect 與 AirPlay 2。而且 Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900 也支援無線連接 Bose 低音箱與環繞聲揚聲器，提供更完整的家庭影院體驗。Soundbar 也能跟 Bose 其他智能揚聲器組成多房間音響系統，同步播放音樂，讓你去到哪個房間都能沉浸在音樂世界中。它亦能透過 Bose SimpleSync，與特定 Bose 耳機包括最新 QuietComfort 45 耳機配對，讓你一個人獨享電影廳視聽體驗。用戶可透過 Bose Music 應用程式，輕鬆設定 Soundbar 或調校各種設定，亦可隨時得到揚聲器的軟件更新。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085928" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_005_RGB.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>Bose 家庭娛樂揚聲器 900 <span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>建議零售價：HK$9,999</p><p>備有黑色、白色可供選擇</p><p>了解更多: <a href="https://bit.ly/35tDSJS">按此</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_01_CMYK-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_01_CMYK-694x481.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="481" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Large-JPG-SB900_Black_01_CMYK-694x481.jpg 694w, https://